promo.summary: Adebayọ ni oun ko mọ wipe asa naa o b'ofin mu o si seleri lati ma se isẹ naa mọ. Nitori Adebayọ, ẹgbẹ to nse ipolongo lodi si didabẹ f'ọmọ obinrin yii se ibẹwo si awọn mii to se bẹẹ wọn si jẹ ko ye wọn, aburu to wa ninu ka maa ge ara ọmọbinrin nitori kaakiri agbaye didabẹ jẹ titẹ ẹtọ awọn obinrin ati ọmọbinrin mọlẹ.

indexImage.caption: Alhaji Adebayo to ndabẹ f'ọmọ obinrin nilu Ilorin
